{
  "id": "adv_group_liz_01_03",
  "title": "LizNoir 01 03",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ…はぁ…",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pant Pant…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.0666666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――三枝にまだ自分はプロレベルに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Rio‚ who had been told by Saegusa that she wasn't",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.2333333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "届いていないと告げられた莉央",
      "translations": {
        "en": "at the professional level yet‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.766666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 8.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……はぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pant…Pant…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――莉央は以前より歌やダンスのレッスンに没頭する",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Rio immersed herself in singing and dancing lessons even more than before‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.333333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "その様子は周囲から見て鬼気迫るほどのものだった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and her efforts were so intense that it was intimidating to watch.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.966666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 18.633333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はい、みんなよくできたわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ everyone‚ you did well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.666666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "十分休憩しましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's take a good break.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 23.833333333333332
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "先生、曲は、流し続けてくれませんか\n私は、まだ踊ります……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sensei‚ could you please keep playing the music?\nI'm going to keep dancing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.933333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 30.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "え？　莉央、貴方は完璧だったわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Rio‚ you were perfect.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "休憩はちゃんと取らないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You need to take a proper break…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 36.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "私は全然、疲れてません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not tired at all!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "練習生A",
      "speakerNameEn": "Trainee",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ちょっと、ちょっと莉央！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hold on‚ hold on‚ Rio!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.233333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "練習生A",
      "speakerNameEn": "Trainee",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "最近、あんた練習しすぎだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You've been practicing too much lately!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "練習生B",
      "speakerNameEn": "Trainee",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そうだよ、体壊したら元も子もないじゃん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right‚ it's no use if you ruin your health!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "練習生B",
      "speakerNameEn": "Trainee",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私達、みんな心配してるんだよ？　何かあったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're all worried about you‚ you know? Did something happen?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 52.666666666666664
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、それは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it's…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.666666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 55.06666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――当初、莉央に風当たりの強かった養成所の候補生たちは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The trainees who were initially harsh towards Rio",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.06666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いつしか莉央を認めるようになっていた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "had come to acknowledge her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――莉央のひたむきに努力する姿、そして実力を見て",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Seeing her dedicated effort and her skills‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "彼女を全員がリスペクトし、気遣っていたのだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "everyone had come to respect and care for her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 69.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "練習生C",
      "speakerNameEn": "Trainee",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "何か不安なことあるなら相談してよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you're worried about something‚ talk to us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "練習生C",
      "speakerNameEn": "Trainee",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "これでも一応、ウチら先輩だしね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're your seniors‚ after all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます\nでも、これは私自身の問題で――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you.\nBut this is my own personal problem――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5133.333333333326,
          "startTime": 79.86666666666666
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 80.06666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "莉央！　すぐに実家に戻るんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio! Go back home right now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "チケットは俺が手配した",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've arranged for your ticket.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_03-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "急に、どうしたんですか？\n三枝さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's going on all of a sudden?\nSaegusa-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 89.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "君のお母さんが、倒れたそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems your mother collapsed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_03-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "――え……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――What…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 95.13333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 95.13333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――岡山のとある病院",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A certain hospital in Okayama.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "莉央の母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……莉央、大げさね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Rio‚ this is too much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "莉央の母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "レッスンを休んでまで帰って来なくても良かったのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You didn't have to come back‚ missing your lessons and all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 104.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_03-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "何言ってるの、お母さんが倒れたのに\nレッスンなんてしてられないわよ……！　ぐすっ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you saying? You collapsed‚ Mom!\nhow could I possibly stay at lessons…? Sob…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "莉央の母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ごめんね、迷惑かけて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry for causing you trouble.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 114.56666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_03-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "……違うわ、謝るのは私よ\nお医者さんが言ってたわ、お母さん極度の過労だって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…No‚ I'm the one who should be apologizing.\nThe doctor said you were extremely overworked.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_03-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "喫茶店も休業して\n沢山パートを掛け持ちしてるって聞いた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You closed the cafe\nand took on multiple part-time jobs‚ I heard…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 129.43333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
